file.name: courses.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  description: "Courses Webservices"
  version: "2.0"
  title: "Courses Webservices"
basePath: "/entity/v1"
paths:
  /courses:
    get:
      summary: "Get a list of available courses."
      description: "Lists all available courses."
      responses:
        200:
          description: "OK"
          schema:
            type: "object"
            properties:
              courses:
                type: "array"
                items:
                  code:
                    type: "string"
                  name:
                    type: "string"
        401:
          description: "Unauthorized"
        403:
          description: "Forbidden"
        404:
          description: "Not Found"
